      <article class="post-891 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-career-services category-kelley-direct category-kelley-school-of-business category-rankings tag-financial-times tag-kelley-direct tag-online-mba tag-ramesh-venkataraman entry" id="post-891" role="article">
       <header class="entry-header">
        <h2 class="h2 entry-title">
         <a href="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/2019/03/04/kelley-direct-online-mba-again-ranked-second-in-the-u-s-and-fourth-worldwide-by-financial-times/" rel="bookmark">
          Kelley Direct Online MBA again ranked second in the U.S. and fourth worldwide by Financial Times
         </a>
        </h2>
        <p class="post-info entry-meta">
         <span class="posted-on">
          Posted on
          <a href="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/2019/03/04/kelley-direct-online-mba-again-ranked-second-in-the-u-s-and-fourth-worldwide-by-financial-times/" rel="bookmark">
           <time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2019-03-04T14:36:15+00:00">
            March 4, 2019
           </time>
          </a>
         </span>
         <span class="byline">
          by
          <span class="entry-author author">
           <a href="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/author/vlahakis/">
            George Vlahakis
           </a>
          </span>
         </span>
        </p>
       </header>
       <section class="entry-content">
        <a href="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/files/2019/02/KSBKDGCSCoaching_20180306_39-17dh93r.jpg">
         <img alt="" class="aligncenter wp-image-894 size-large" height="365" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" src="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/files/2019/02/KSBKDGCSCoaching_20180306_39-17dh93r-1024x584.jpg" srcset="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/files/2019/02/KSBKDGCSCoaching_20180306_39-17dh93r-1024x584.jpg 1024w, https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/files/2019/02/KSBKDGCSCoaching_20180306_39-17dh93r-300x171.jpg 300w, https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/files/2019/02/KSBKDGCSCoaching_20180306_39-17dh93r-768x438.jpg 768w" width="640"/>
        </a>
        <p>
        </p>
        <p>
         BLOOMINGTON, Ind. – Kelley Direct students here for
         <a href="https://kelley.iu.edu/programs/online/student-life/kelley-connect-weeks.cshtml">
          Kelley Connect Week
         </a>
         received some additional good news Monday, when they learned along with the rest of the business school about new rankings from the Financial Times, which again
         <a href="http://rankings.ft.com/businessschoolrankings/online-mba-ranking-2019">
          ranked the program fourth worldwide and second among U.S. institutions
         </a>
         .
        </p>
        <p>
         One of several top-rated offerings of the Indiana University
         <a href="https://kelley.iu.edu/">
          Kelley School of Business
         </a>
         , Kelley Direct a year ago moved up into those positions in FT’s rankings and has maintained them within a competitive field. While the top four programs in FT’s rankings of online MBA programs remain unchanged, there were many shifts among schools in the top 10 and beyond.
        </p>
        <p>
         In addition,
         <a href="https://kelley.iu.edu/programs/online/degrees/index.cshtml">
          Kelley Direct
         </a>
         was No. 1 overall in terms of research rank and online delivery and its career services were ranked second.
        </p>
        <p>
         <a class="more-link" href="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/2019/03/04/kelley-direct-online-mba-again-ranked-second-in-the-u-s-and-fourth-worldwide-by-financial-times/#more-891">
          <span aria-label="Continue reading Kelley Direct Online MBA again ranked second in the U.S. and fourth worldwide by Financial Times">
           (more…)
          </span>
         </a>
        </p>
        <div addthis:title="Kelley Direct Online MBA again ranked second in the U.S. and fourth worldwide by Financial Times " addthis:url="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/2019/03/04/kelley-direct-online-mba-again-ranked-second-in-the-u-s-and-fourth-worldwide-by-financial-times/" class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style ">
         <a class="addthis_button_facebook_like" fb:like:layout="button_count">
         </a>
         <a class="addthis_button_tweet">
         </a>
         <a class="addthis_counter addthis_pill_style">
         </a>
        </div>
       </section>
