      <article class="post-760 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-32-program category-accounting category-careers category-consulting category-degrees category-gap category-guest-speakers category-pwc tag-capitol-hill tag-david-greene tag-mitch-mcconnell tag-patrick-hopkins tag-pwc tag-rohit-kumar tag-tax-consulting tag-tax-policy tag-taxes entry" id="post-760" role="article">
       <header class="entry-header">
        <h2 class="h2 entry-title">
         <a href="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/2018/12/13/pwcs-kumar-shares-an-insiders-view-of-washington-and-policymaking-to-students-in-kelleys-graduate-accounting-programs/" rel="bookmark">
          PwC’s Kumar shares an insider’s view of Washington and policymaking to students in Kelley’s graduate accounting programs
         </a>
        </h2>
        <p class="post-info entry-meta">
         <span class="posted-on">
          Posted on
          <a href="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/2018/12/13/pwcs-kumar-shares-an-insiders-view-of-washington-and-policymaking-to-students-in-kelleys-graduate-accounting-programs/" rel="bookmark">
           <time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2018-12-13T15:55:24+00:00">
            December 13, 2018
           </time>
          </a>
         </span>
         <span class="byline">
          by
          <span class="entry-author author">
           <a href="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/author/vlahakis/">
            George Vlahakis
           </a>
          </span>
         </span>
        </p>
       </header>
       <section class="entry-content">
        <a href="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/files/2018/12/KSBKSBRohitKumar_20181210_017-13a3t6p.jpg">
         <img alt="" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-765" height="404" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" src="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/files/2018/12/KSBKSBRohitKumar_20181210_017-13a3t6p-1024x647.jpg" srcset="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/files/2018/12/KSBKSBRohitKumar_20181210_017-13a3t6p-1024x647.jpg 1024w, https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/files/2018/12/KSBKSBRohitKumar_20181210_017-13a3t6p-300x190.jpg 300w, https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/files/2018/12/KSBKSBRohitKumar_20181210_017-13a3t6p-768x486.jpg 768w" width="640"/>
        </a>
        <p>
        </p>
        <p>
         BLOOMINGTON, Ind. – Indiana University’s Kelley School of Business and its
         <a href="https://kelley.iu.edu/programs/3-2-mba/index.cshtml">
          3/2 MBA Program
         </a>
         welcomed
         <a href="https://www.pwc.com/us/en/contacts/r/rohit-kumar.html">
          Rohit Kumar
         </a>
         , a principal at PwC LLP and leader of the firm’s tax policy services group in its Washington National Tax Services practice.
        </p>
        <p>
         Kumar provided a unique perspective. He has extensive knowledge of government and public policy. Before joining
         <a href="https://www.pwc.com/us/en.html">
          PwC
         </a>
         in 2013, he worked closely with three Senate leaders on Capitol Hill, including seven years with current Majority Leader Mitch McConnell, for whom he served as domestic policy director and deputy chief of staff.
        </p>
        <p>
         He helped to develop and implement tax, trade, budget and health care policy for McConnell as well as former Sens. Trent Lott, Bill Frist and Phil Gramm.
        </p>
        <p>
         Kumar met with
         <a href="https://kelley.iu.edu/">
          Kelley
         </a>
         students on Dec. 10 and discussed an understanding of policy issues as crucial to many companies, particularly as they develop strategies from both a technical and political perspective. PwC recruits at Kelley, particularly students in the 3/2 MBA Program, which offers them an understanding of accounting principles combined with business fundamentals.
        </p>
        <p>
         This was the first time Kumar has visited a business school in his current leadership role at PwC.
        </p>
        <p>
         <a class="more-link" href="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/2018/12/13/pwcs-kumar-shares-an-insiders-view-of-washington-and-policymaking-to-students-in-kelleys-graduate-accounting-programs/#more-760">
          <span aria-label="Continue reading PwC’s Kumar shares an insider’s view of Washington and policymaking to students in Kelley’s graduate accounting programs">
           (more…)
          </span>
         </a>
        </p>
        <div addthis:title="PwC’s Kumar shares an insider’s view of Washington and policymaking to students in Kelley’s graduate accounting programs " addthis:url="https://blog.kelley.iu.edu/2018/12/13/pwcs-kumar-shares-an-insiders-view-of-washington-and-policymaking-to-students-in-kelleys-graduate-accounting-programs/" class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style ">
         <a class="addthis_button_facebook_like" fb:like:layout="button_count">
         </a>
